{"head":{"layout":"RulePage","next":"/user-guide/rules/unit-no-unknown/","prev":"/user-guide/rules/unit-blacklist/","description":"unit-case Specify lowercase or uppercase for units. Options string: \"lower\"|\"upper\" \"lower\" The following patterns are considered…","title":"unit-case"},"body":"<h1 id=\"unit-case\"><a href=\"#unit-case\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>unit-case</h1>\n<p>Specify lowercase or uppercase for units.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\">    <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">10px</span>; }\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**              ↑\n *     These units */</span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"options\"><a href=\"#options\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>Options</h2>\n<p><code>string</code>: <code>\"lower\"|\"upper\"</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"lower\"><a href=\"#lower\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a><code>\"lower\"</code></h3>\n<p>The following patterns are considered violations:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">10PX</span>;\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">10Px</span>;\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">10pX</span>;\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>PIXEL;\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">calc</span>(10PX * 2);\n}</code></pre>\n<p>The following patterns are <em>not</em> considered violations:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">10px</span>;\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">calc</span>(10px * 2);\n}</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"upper\"><a href=\"#upper\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a><code>\"upper\"</code></h3>\n<p>The following patterns are considered violations:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">10px</span>;\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">10Px</span>;\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">10pX</span>;\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>pixel;\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">calc</span>(10px * 2);\n}</code></pre>\n<p>The following patterns are <em>not</em> considered violations:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">10PX</span>;\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">calc</span>(10PX * 2);\n}</code></pre>\n","__filename":"user-guide/rules/unit-case.md","__url":"/user-guide/rules/unit-case/","__resourceUrl":"/user-guide/rules/unit-case/index.html","__dataUrl":"/user-guide/rules/unit-case/index.html.4dc70441e46270b8b77f0ffb604e2d35.json"}